[u]On Foot:[/u]
- Left Stick - Movement
- Real Crouch - Crouch
- [Not in VR] - Jump
- A - Sprint
- B - Toggle flashlight
- X (hold) - Cops Lock car
- Left Stick In - Map
- Y - Toggle HUD (_Better FPS on Quest with HUD off_)

[u]In Car:[/u]
- Left Stick - Movement
- Left Trigger - Honk Horn
- A - Get in or out of car
- Right Trigger - Break Car